<div class="main">
   <h1 class="title">Make a reservation for your lesson.</h1> 
        <p class="subtitle">Your lesson is shown below, confirm your lesson if there are no problems.</p>
<hr size="1px">
    <div class="main-left">
         <img class="Profile-photo" src="<%="/conversation.jpg"%>"><br>
